idea-plugin.description:
Code submission template used by Starcor company
     <p>使用以下模板创建提交消息:</p>
    <pre>
    &lt;Title(feat|fix|optimization...):({id}) {summary} &gt;
    &lt;Cause: &gt;
    &lt;Solution：&gt;
    &lt;Effect：&gt;
    &lt;Reviewer：&gt;
    </pre>

   Plugin for Meson syntax highlight support.<br><br>

   Plugin is <b>free</b> for community/free IDEs: IntelliJ IDEA Community, Android Studio, etc. <br>
   Plugin is <b>paid</b> for commercial IDEs: IntelliJ IDEA Ultimate, CLion, etc. <br><br>

   <li> Basic syntax highlight by https://mesonbuild.com/Syntax.html;
   </li><li> Basic type checks for returning objects from functions and methods by https://mesonbuild.com/Reference-manual.html;
   </li><li> Highlighting styles are customisable at Settings -&gt; Editor -&gt; Color Scheme -&gt; Meson. <br><br>

   Known limitations aka Plans for future [no commitments ;)] :
   </li><li> Parsing process is slow on relatively large (&gt;1k lines) meson.build files (like systemd's <a href="https://github.com/systemd/systemd/blob/master/meson.build">meson.build</a>);
   </li><li> No type checks for variables; Just some type checks for returning objects from methods. <br><br>


</li>

