idea-plugin.description:
Auto-Align allows you to align your code with a pretty print alignment 
<br> 
<br> SHORTCUT : (windows/linux) CONTROL+OPTION+I (mac) CMD+OPTION+I 
<br> 
<br> EXAMPLE : 
<br> 
<pre>
var hi={
  field : 'val',
  heel: 'red'
};
var hi    = {
  field    : 'val',
  heel     : 'red'
};
      <pre></pre></pre>

idea-plugin.change-notes:
      - Special symbols in strings have same color but are bold;
- Constants are not bold;
- Number literals have the same color as string literals;
- XML, JSON, YAML &amp; Dockerfile color schemes are reworked to look like C# color scheme.
